        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33403586/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33403586/" class="">第104页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3175914/" class=" " title="素位时中">素位时中</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33403586">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">第8行关于圣道明的卒年“1121”应为“1221”</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-11-13 18:33</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                第8行关于圣道明的卒年“1121”应为“1221”
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

